FBIS3-3340 "drchi054_d_94016" FBIS-CHI-94-054 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Mar 1994 Northeast Asia Li Peng Hosts Ceremony OW1903120094 Beijing Central People's Radio Network in Mandarin 1030 GMT 19 Mar 94 OW1903120094 Beijing Central People's Radio Network Language: Mandarin Article Type:BFN [From the "National Hookup" program] [Text] Premier Li Peng presided over a ceremony at the Central Hall of the Great Hall of the People this evening in honor of Japanese Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa, who is on an official visit to China. Qian Qichen, vice premier and foreign minister, and others were present at the welcoming ceremony. After the ceremony, Premier Li Peng and Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa held a friendly conversation. Following that, Li Peng hosted a banquet in honor of Prime Minister Hosokawa and Mrs. Hosokawa. Prime Minister Hosokawa and his entourage arrived in Beijing around noon today. Chen Jinhua, minister in charge of the State Planning Commission and chairman of the Chinese Reception Committee; Xu Dunxin, Chinese ambassador to Japan; Vice Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan; and Japanese Ambassador to China Michihiko Kunihiro greeted him at the airport.
